      <Properties>
        <Configuration>
          <Text>- Join orders to product context by ProductID,
  then add regional targets by Region.
- Calculate revenue exposure, late flags,
  gross margin value, and a simple priority score.
- Summarize by Region and Category so leaders
  can review the highest-value lanes first.</Text>
          <Font name="Segoe UI" size="8.25" style="0" />
          <TextColor r="0" g="0" b="0" />
